init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You think to yourself, "I'm sure this is just a prank, but I'll play along."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The phone rings a few times, and then a voice answers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I need you to come to Nebraska, and meet me at my house."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: , you pack your bags and head to the airport.

actions.text: "Ah, Mr. Obama, it's a pleasure to meet you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That's what the public was told, but it's a lie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "This is my work room, where I conduct my work for the government.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You open the folder, and see the picture of a man, with a face that looks like a cross between a human and an alien.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are Barack Obama, and you are the leader of the task force to combat the alien threat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be the one to lead the world in the fight against the alien threat.
